  "text": "Digital watermarking schemes have been under research and development for various types of multimedia data for many years, including audio formats like PCM, mp3 or MIDI. In this work we focus on digital PCM audio data. Several approaches for PCM audio watermarking have been introduced in the literature, like in [CITATION_1] , in [5] or [10] .",
